text: Goeridae is a family of caddisflies in the order Trichoptera. There are about 12 genera and at least 160 described species in Goeridae. The type genus for Goeridae is Goera J.F. Stephens, 1829. ==Genera== ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * Category:Trichoptera families Category:Integripalpia
